Night Catches Us;;66;;81;;R;;When ex-Black Panther Marcus (Anthony Mackie) returns to Philadelphia for the funeral of his father, he knows it's not going to be an easy visit. Many of his old radical friends, including "DoRight" Miller (Jamie Hector), still believe that Marcus was responsible for the death of a Panther leader right before he took off. While trying to convince everyone he's not a snitch, Marcus rekindles his relationship with Patricia (Kerry Washington), the widow of the slain leader.;;Drama;;Tanya Hamilton;;2010;;Anthony Mackie,Kerry Washington,Jamie Hector,Wendell Pierce,Jamara Griffin,Amari Cheatom,Jann Ellis,Damali Mason;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/night_catches_us